NB. =========================================================
NB.*clean v clean y to tolerance of x (default 1e_10)
NB. form: tolerance (default 1e_10) clean numbers
NB. sets values less than tolerance to 0
clean=: 1e_10&$: : (4 : 0)
if. L. y do.
  x clean each y
else.
  if. (3!:0 y) e. 16 16384 do.
    j./"1 y * (2*x) <: | y=. +.y
  else.
    y * x <: |y
  end.
end.
)

